KUSHAQEKE abaningi abalalele icala lokubulawa kukaSenzo Meyiwa, u-Advocate Malesela Teffo eveza ukuthi ngubani owabulala unozinti weBafa Bafana ne-Orlando Pirates. UTeffo uveze ukuthi unofakazi owazibonela konke okwenzeka ngosuku lwesigameko, othi uNonhlanhla Kelly Khumalo wuyena owadubula uSenzo ngephutha. “Kunofakazi owazibonela ngawakhe, ozoveza ukuthi uSenzo Meyiwa wabulawa ngokudutshulwa nguNonhlanhla Kelly Khumalo ngephutha.” “Lo fakazi uzoqhubeka aveze ukuthi isibhamu adubula ngaso uSenzo wasithatha kuLongwe Twala naye owayekhona endlini.” Abantu basale bebambe ongezansi ngalolu daba, abaningi bathi akuboshwe bonke abebesendini ukuze kuzophuma iqiniso. "I put it to you Mr Mosia that a witness, not just a witness, an eyewitness will testify that Senzo Robert Meyiwa was allegedly shot by Nonhlanhla Kelly Khumalo by mistake, as it's alleged," says Adv. Malesela Teffo.#Newzroom405 #SenzoMeyiwatrial #SenzoMeyiwa pic.twitter.com/o4d6qYyJsb Phindile Nxumalo: Ngiyamethemba Kelly akasoze ayenza into enjenga le izandla zakhe zihlanzekile. Phindy Qwabe: Hawu cha ngaze ngaphoxeka sengamkhulumela kangaka uKelly. Cyril Vusumuzi Majola: Ubaba kaSenzo waze washona ethi uKelly ubulele umfana wakhe. Saphika thina esithanda uKelly. Kunjani uma kunje. Fezile Angel Mthembu: Kuthiwa ayinuki ingosiwe. Ave esengozini kodwa uTeffo benofakazi wakhe owazibonela.